story.title: The XY Experiments - Part 1
story.storyDescription: Eve thought her sister had gone missing...until she found a clone of her.

messages.text: Eve, are you there??
Hey
You can stop picking out pics for your sis’s memorial
What are you talking about
I just saw her
Don’t fucking joke with me, Anna, I can’t take it
It’s not a joke. This man just led her into a condo
PICK UP THE PHONE
I’m trying to be quiet and see what’s going on inside
WHERE ARE YOU??
Garden Plaza.
Are you sure it’s her??
It’s totally her
Did you call Missing Persons and the cops???
Yes! Of course I did
Oh my God, I’m crying. I’m calling my Dad and Mom
Okay…
Was he hurting her??
He was kind of tugging at her arm and dragging her, but she looked okay
I’m going to kill him with my bare hands.
Cops will take care of it
I’m in my car right now coming over
They should be here by the time you’re here, but be careful
Do you see anything??
I’m going around the back. I’m almost there
And???
Anna??
Something really strange is going on
WHAT DO YOU MEAN??
The guy is armed, and there’s a chick in army fatigues…
There are a bunch of girls in there. Like seven
WHAT ABOUT ADRIENNE? What’s going on with her???
Oh my God
WHAT
They just turned around
Did something bad happen to them??
Eve…they all look like Adrienne.
What the hell are you talking about?
There are seven girls who look like your sister. Different hair styles, but all look exactly like her
This is the most insane thing I’ve ever seen
She doesn’t have any other sisters. Just me
Are you sure about that??
OF COURSE I’M SURE
Well, what I’m seeing doesn’t correspond with what you’re saying
I DON’T GIVE A SHIT! CAN YOU GET HER OUT OF THERE???
I don’t know, I’m trying to think how to create a diversion
SHIT! One of them just took the gun from the guy and shot him!
IS HE DEAD?
Anna??
What’s happening??
ANNA???
PICK UP YOUR PHONE
ANNA, IS SHE OKAY???
twenty minutes later
Eve…
WHERE DID YOU GO??? WHAT HAPPENED??
You need to listen to me here. The government is in on this somehow
In on what??
The cops never came. These guys in black SUVs did. Four or five of them
How would they have known to come if it weren’t for me calling?
WHAT?? WHERE’S MY SISTER??
Just stay away from here. Adrienne says they’ll know who you are
She’s okay??? I’m not staying away!  What else did she say??
Not much, and we’re not even at the complex anymore. We’re headed south
You got away??
No. I’m in the back of one of the SUVs right now
WHAT!? HOW!? WHERE IS ADRIENNE??
She’s in the other one with the rest of the girls
I don’t think we’re going anywhere good
I don’t understand, are you hiding out in the trunk??!!
In plain sight
After the guy got shot, the army guard pulled out her gun on them.
I snuck in the back door, and knocked her out
HOLY SHIT
Everyone was scrambling to get out, one of the girls actually escaped, before these guys busted through the front door
Adrienne helped me drag the guard into the closet, where we tied her up, and I put on her fatigues...
and pretended to march her out before they dragged her out
So you’re pretending to be the guard right now??
Yes.
Who are the people in your car with you??
I don’t know yet. They’ve been silent. One guy keeps talking in code on a walkie talkie
Something about Project XY
Aren’t they going to catch you??
I know what it’s like to lose a sibling. I’m going to get your sister back to you.
Shit, I have to go
Wait!
Anna??
Click below to see what happens next...
